=REQUIREMENTS

You will need all of these
  Perl
  GhostScript (with fonts)
  Netpbm (with pnmrotate)
  MoreUtils (for sponge)
  libSixel (with libpng support)
  ImageMagick
  a suitable Terminal Program

Note the method to get the above depends on your platform.
Please see the detail for each platform below.

=STEPS

./configure.sh
make
make check
sudo make install

----------------------------

=CYGWIN

setup-x86_64.exe
  ghostscript libgs9 ghostscript-fonts-other
  netpbm libnetpbm10
	ImageMagick
  moreutils
  mintty
  
From-Source
  https://github.com/saitoha/libsixel
   
=LINUX (DEBIAN)

apt
  ghostscript ghostscript-x gsfonts gsfonts-other gsfonts-x11
	ImageMagick
  moreutils
  libsixel-bin (default version missing libpng support)
  mlterm

dpkg From-External-Repository
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/netpbm

=macOS

port
  netpbm
  ghostscript
	ImageMagick
  moreutils
	bash (modern version)

From-Source
  https://github.com/saitoha/libsixel

From App Store
  iTerm2



